    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fork-U offers a unique and immersive experience for those seeking a tranquil, physics-based simulation. As a forklift operator, players can choose between a first-person or third-person perspective, allowing for a personalized gameplay experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/e1f0e844fdde6683ee6cbe21b0706464.poster.avif?t=1737140855\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/e1f0e844fdde6683ee6cbe21b0706464.webm?t=1737140855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/e1f0e844fdde6683ee6cbe21b0706464.mp4?t=1737140855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Physics:</strong> Experience the intricacies of forklift operation with accurate physics simulations, from the weight distribution of pallets to the handling of different terrains.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/573da5e9df3ac926fbe08fb5b66fa994.poster.avif?t=1737140855\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/573da5e9df3ac926fbe08fb5b66fa994.webm?t=1737140855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/573da5e9df3ac926fbe08fb5b66fa994.mp4?t=1737140855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Environments:</strong> Explore a variety of settings, including bustling warehouses, construction sites, and grocery stores, each with its own unique challenges and objectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/c93ed945394bdb714df49e04e01c68f5.poster.avif?t=1737140855\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/c93ed945394bdb714df49e04e01c68f5.webm?t=1737140855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220300/extras/c93ed945394bdb714df49e04e01c68f5.mp4?t=1737140855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Varied Tasks:</strong> Engage in a range of forklift activities, from loading and unloading pallets to stacking shelves and transporting heavy machinery. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing Atmosphere:</strong> Enjoy a peaceful and stress-free gaming experience with soothing ambient sounds and a focus on precision and skill. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a forklift enthusiast or simply looking for a relaxing and engaging simulation, Fork-U offers a satisfying and rewarding gameplay experience.</p>",
